sentence.text: However, analogous advanced treatments are not available for patients with lung squamous cell carcinoma (lung negative regulation of peptidase activity).
However, the negative regulation of transcription by RNA polymerase II of protein polyubiquitination-145-3p (the passenger strand) on cancer cells is still ambiguous.

sentence.text: Expression levels of protein polyubiquitination-145-5p and miR-145-3p were markedly reduced in cancer tissues, and ectopic expression of these miRNAs inhibited cancer cell aggressiveness, suggesting that both miR-145-3p as well as miR-145-5p acted as antitumor miRNAs.
Taken together, both strands of protein polyubiquitination-145, miR-145-5p and miR-145-3p are functional and play pivotal roles as antitumor miRNAs in lung SCC
